Kanaiyazhi, a pure tamil word of ancient origin, is a  [[signet ring]]. It was used by indian kings for authenticating ambassdors and official persons.

Kanaiyazhi-ONE is a conception for human identification system  more then one billon people in India to resemble past historic period and much better design compare then Malaysia's [[MyKad]]


